parameters:
Ha... There doesn't seem to be any significant changes. The
magic restraints are functioning without any issues.

\SE[52]Yes, thank you. \!\SE[3]May I have a little chat with
you?

\SE[2]It's been a while, Lunaroa. \SE[3]...I wonder when was
the last time we met.

\SE[47]...I guess it's been about half a year. \SE[48]I
never thought I would meet you again in this way, Vega.
\SE[58]...What happened to Laura and the others?

\SE[74]You can rest assured. \.You're in a better state than
I am. \!\SE[3]...Do you understand the charges against you
correctly?

\SE[2]A terrorist act planning to disable the school's
functions. \SE[3]You are also suspected of attempted murder
of the faculty and the burning of Hatayaki Village.

\SE[47]...Quite an impressive background. It's almost like
I'm not being treated as a criminal.

\SE[76]It seems like the honored scholarship student is
quite scary to the people in the upper echelons of the
school. \SE[51]...They seem to want to create that kind of
script.

\SE[4]Hey, you. \SE[3]I want to have a little conversation
with her, just us girls...
\SE[50]...I'm sorry. I was sleeping a little.

\SE[7]What exactly do you intend to do? At this rate, you
too...

\SE[3]There's something I want to show you ahead. Come with
me.

\SE[12]...Wait. We have to help Laura and Vita. \SE[13]
That's the minimum requirement.

\SE[74]...Don't worry. \SE[3]Their separate cells are along
the way. \SE[3]I plan to pick them up while we're at it.

It seems like a portable toilet. Are they expecting me to
use it here?
\SE I'm sorry, but I'd rather die...
